commit.title: [termops] Move simultaneous term decomposition functions to library
commit.message:
[termops] Move simultaneous term decomposition functions to library

This is an attempt to cleanup / unify the two implementations of
`shrink` in Coq. Abstract and Equations use the one in Declare,
obligations uses its own.

More work is needed to understand the desired semantics here, but
a general API should be possible.
